Dialogue: 3,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.46,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,怎么说我们要怎么走啊
Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.46,0:00:02.36,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我们是 我们是
Dialogue: 3,0:00:02.36,0:00:03.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我们是在月球的什么
Dialogue: 3,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.03,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,这是我们的飞船吗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:05.03,0:00:06.06,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我们要下飞船是吗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.00,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,月球的空间站
Dialogue: 3,0:00:08.00,0:00:08.88,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎 好像这可以
Dialogue: 3,0:00:08.88,0:00:09.58,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,可以按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.60,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎按一下
Dialogue: 3,0:00:11.13,0:00:11.36,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 3,0:00:11.36,0:00:12.66,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,两个人一起吗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:12.66,0:00:13.50,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎哎哦
Dialogue: 3,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.36,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哦哦哎
Dialogue: 3,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.10,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎哎
Dialogue: 3,0:00:15.10,0:00:15.74,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,你按那个呀
Dialogue: 3,0:00:15.74,0:00:16.73,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,你按那个呀
Dialogue: 3,0:00:17.07,0:00:17.75,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎哎
Dialogue: 3,0:00:17.75,0:00:18.93,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,按住不动
Dialogue: 3,0:00:18.93,0:00:19.71,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,开了吗
Dialogue: 3,0:00:19.71,0:00:20.00,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 3,0:00:20.00,0:00:20.70,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,这底下开了
Dialogue: 3,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.57,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,开了开了开了
Dialogue: 3,0:00:22.59,0:00:22.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 3,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.80,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,这里有故事
Dialogue: 3,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.10,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,就在刚刚
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.50,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,一场流星风暴
Dialogue: 3,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.03,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,把朗月生物公司轰成了渣
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.03,0:00:28.63,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,所有人
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.56,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,唯独二位
Dialogue: 3,0:00:29.56,0:00:30.29,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,就我们两个正“忙”得不可开交
Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.29,0:00:30.94,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,养殖的史莱姆趁机“越狱”
Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.94,0:00:31.23,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,还顺带感染了
Dialogue: 3,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.35,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,月球联合神经代理人（L.U.N.A.）
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.35,0:00:32.94,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,*朗月黑话*
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.94,0:00:33.87,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,她现在已经彻底疯了
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.87,0:00:34.34,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,唯一的出路就是
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.34,0:00:34.77,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,冲进她的服务器设施
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.77,0:00:36.05,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,应急逃生火箭就停在哪里
Dialogue: 3,0:00:36.05,0:00:36.93,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,啊 就我们
Dialogue: 3,0:00:36.93,0:00:37.96,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,*组织语言*
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.00,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,要找到火箭
Dialogue: 3,0:00:39.00,0:00:39.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 3,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.41,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,找到火箭然后发射
Dialogue: 3,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.13,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,把我们自己发射出去是吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.13,0:00:43.99,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.99,0:00:44.98,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,差不多是这个意思
Dialogue: 3,0:00:44.98,0:00:45.37,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.37,0:00:45.89,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,开吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.89,0:00:46.43,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 3,0:00:46.43,0:00:47.49,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,两个人同时按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.00,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.00,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.15,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 3,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.35,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.35,0:00:52.86,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,1按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.86,0:00:53.66,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 3,0:00:53.92,0:00:54.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,321
Dialogue: 3,0:00:54.90,0:00:55.56,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.14,0:00:55.94,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,按
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.40,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 3,0:00:57.40,0:00:58.31,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,我摁了呀
Dialogue: 3,0:00:58.31,0:00:59.60,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,我摁了呀
Dialogue: 3,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.50,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,是不是这边的线有问题啊
Dialogue: 3,0:01:03.93,0:01:04.72,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,嗷嗷 我知
Dialogue: 3,0:01:04.72,0:01:05.53,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.31,0:01:06.83,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎等一下
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.03,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我们好像可以直接下去
Dialogue: 3,0:01:08.03,0:01:09.03,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,这是什么呀
Dialogue: 3,0:01:09.60,0:01:10.40,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,阀门缺了
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.09,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,缺了个阀门
Dialogue: 3,0:01:11.95,0:01:12.86,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,没阀门
Dialogue: 3,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.03,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,有异物卡住了机械装置
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.63,0:01:17.74,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,机械装置在哪
Dialogue: 3,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.39,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎 这是阀门吧
Dialogue: 3,0:01:22.55,0:01:23.55,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎这个开了
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.10,0:01:26.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 3,0:01:26.90,0:01:27.73,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哇 核按钮
Dialogue: 3,0:01:27.73,0:01:29.59,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我得一直在转
Dialogue: 3,0:01:30.20,0:01:31.73,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,啊 那我把这个开开
Dialogue: 3,0:01:32.40,0:01:33.26,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,OK这个也开了
Dialogue: 3,0:01:33.26,0:01:34.05,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,来来来
Dialogue: 3,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.53,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,一块按核按钮
Dialogue: 3,0:01:36.93,0:01:37.68,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,按了
Dialogue: 3,0:01:38.20,0:01:38.66,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 3,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.10,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 3,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.52,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,开了开了
Dialogue: 3,0:01:40.80,0:01:41.86,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,这还核按钮
Dialogue: 3,0:01:41.86,0:01:42.98,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,原来不是发射核弹
Dialogue: 3,0:01:43.70,0:01:44.59,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,只要不影响
Dialogue: 3,0:01:44.59,0:01:45.81,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,史莱姆捕猎指标
Dialogue: 3,0:01:45.81,0:01:46.83,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,辩论有益身心
Dialogue: 3,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.83,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我们等下不会有怪吧
Dialogue: 3,0:01:48.83,0:01:49.50,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 3,0:01:49.50,0:01:49.92,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 3,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.20,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,下去了下去了
Dialogue: 3,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.18,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,应该会给我们武器的
Dialogue: 3,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.88,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 3,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.66,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,@在吗
Dialogue: 3,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.03,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,*至尊大空间尊享体验*
Dialogue: 3,0:02:04.26,0:02:04.83,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 3,0:02:05.73,0:02:06.14,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 3,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.83,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我帮你把马桶盖给翻开了
Dialogue: 3,0:02:09.03,0:02:09.83,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 3,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.95,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 3,0:02:16.79,0:02:17.40,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 3,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.76,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,我为什么上不了呢
Dialogue: 3,0:02:18.76,0:02:19.83,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎你别动你别动
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.83,0:02:20.66,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,别动 背对着我
Dialogue: 3,0:02:20.66,0:02:22.06,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,背对着我 背对着我
Dialogue: 3,0:02:22.06,0:02:22.56,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎站起来
Dialogue: 3,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.36,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,站起来站起来
Dialogue: 3,0:02:23.96,0:02:24.90,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎好
Dialogue: 3,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.06,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 3,0:02:28.06,0:02:28.80,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,什么说法
Dialogue: 3,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.29,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我戳了一下
Dialogue: 3,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.50,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,你对你对我做了什么
Dialogue: 3,0:02:32.16,0:02:32.73,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 3,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.66,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,有两个马桶
Dialogue: 3,0:02:33.66,0:02:34.47,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,来来来
Dialogue: 3,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.33,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,你上一个
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.33,0:02:36.20,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,我上一个
Dialogue: 3,0:02:36.20,0:02:36.82,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,然后咱俩一块
Dialogue: 3,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.13,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,按这个马桶按钮
Dialogue: 3,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.13,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,你好了吗
Dialogue: 3,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.40,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,321
Dialogue: 3,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.13,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,按
Dialogue: 3,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.06,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎没反应啊
Dialogue: 3,0:02:45.06,0:02:45.80,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,没反应吗
Dialogue: 3,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.23,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,没反应没反应
Dialogue: 3,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.26,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,什么说法走
Dialogue: 3,0:02:53.80,0:02:54.93,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,必须得按吗
Dialogue: 3,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.73,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,舱门上锁
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.33,0:03:00.52,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,他上锁了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.86,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎这边有个按钮
Dialogue: 3,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.63,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 3,0:03:03.93,0:03:04.63,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,掀开
Dialogue: 3,0:03:05.69,0:03:07.03,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,要掀开
Dialogue: 3,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.13,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.13,0:03:10.62,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,要放下
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.13,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,要把马桶盖放下
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.13,0:03:12.93,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,ah
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.20,0:03:17.69,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,啊开了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.86,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,开了开了开了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.86,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,哎开了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.00,0:03:19.40,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,你刚没
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.66,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,你没蹲下去
Dialogue: 3,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.33,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,你拉屎是站着拉的是吧
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.63,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,我蹲下去了呀
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.60,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,你刚不是看着我蹲的吗
Dialogue: 3,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.27,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 3,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.20,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,第二关
Dialogue: 3,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.20,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 3,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.66,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,我们开始有血量了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.20,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,完了氧气怎么
Dialogue: 3,0:03:31.20,0:03:31.89,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.33,q3,atg2,0,0,0,,开始有压迫感了
Dialogue: 3,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.30,DJK,atg1,0,0,0,,有氧气
